webdavmanager: Name of the a special page that allows management of the WebDAV entry point
webdav-ns-main: Label for the main namespace. This is also used as a folder name so it must not contain any invalid filesystem characters
webdav-default-edit-comment: Text of the edit comment in revision history in case a user edits a page with WebDAV
webdav-default-delete-comment: Text of the edit comment in revision history in case a user deletes a page with WebDAV
webdav-default-move-comment: Text of the edit comment in revision history in case a user renames a page with WebDAV
webdav-statictoken-prefs: Label of a field on [[Special:Preferences]] that shows the access URL for an user
webdav-statictoken-prefs-help: Help text of a field on [[Special:Preferences]] that shows the access URL for an user
